Nonando ongaaka , Kalunga okwe mu yumudha , nokonima yomasiku 40 okwa londo e ta yi megulu .
Ehokololo ndika ekumithi otali adhika mOmavaangeli gane gomOmanyolo gopaKriste gOshigreka , ngoka hagi ithanwa Etestamendi Epe .
( 1 Aakorinto 15 : 14 ) Ngele oya ningwa shili , nena aantu oye na onakuyiwa ombwanawa , ndjoka nangoye to ka vula okukala wu na .
Mbela Omavaangeli , omahokololo goshili nenge ogiifundja ?
Omahokololo gOmavaangeli otagu ulike kutya oga nyolwa lela mondjila nuuyelele awuhe owa tulwa mo .
Pashiholelwa , omu na oondumba dhomadhina gomahala golela , ngoka ogendji kunena haga vulu okutalelwa po .
Otaga popi kombinga yaantu yoshili , oshinima shoka sha kolekwa kaanandjokonona . — Lukas 3 : 1 , 2 , 23 .
Jesus okwa popiwa kaanyoli mboka ya li ko omimvo 2 000 nasha lwaampono dhaka pita .
* Omukalo moka Jesus a li a dhipagwa , ngaashi gwa hokololwa mOmavaangeli , ogwa fa ngoka gwa li hagu longithwa muRoma pethimbo ndyoka .
Shimwe ishewe , iiningwanima mbyoka ya li ya ningwa po oya hokololwa paushili , mwa kwatelwa nomapuko ngoka aalongwa yaJesus ya li ya ningi .
( Mateus 26 : 56 ; Lukas 22 : 24 - 26 ; Johannes 18 : 10 , 11 ) Iinima ayihe mbika otayi ulike kutya aanyoli yOmavaangeli oya nyola iinima yi li paushili noyolela kombinga yaJesus .
Nonando aantu oye shi zimina kutya Jesus oko a li e ta si , yamwe ohaya kala ya limbililwa kombinga yeyumuko lye .
Nokuli naayapostoli ye kaya li ye shi itaale sho yu uvu tango kutya okwa yumuka .
( Lukas 24 : 11 ) Oya ka za owala momalimbililo sho yo nosho wo aalongwa yalwe ya mono Jesus lwiikando .
Oshikando shimwe okwa li a monika koonzapo dhi vulithe 500 . — 1 Aakorinto 15 : 6 .
Pethimbo sho Jesus a kwatwa po nokudhipagwa , aalongwa Ye oya li taya uvithile ayehe nuulaadhi kombinga yeyumuko lye nokuli naamboka ya li ye mu dhipaga .
( Iilonga 4 : 1 - 3 , 10 , 19 , 20 ; 5 : 27 - 32 ) Mbela aalongwa oyendji oya li ngaa taye ku uvitha nuulaadhi ngele kaya li lelalela ye na uushili kutya Jesus okwa yumuka ?
Eeno . Eyumuko lyaJesus oli li oshinima shoka sha li sha humitha komeho Uukriste pethimbo lyonale nosho wo kunena .
Omahokololo gOmavaangeli ngoka taga popi kombinga yeso neyumuko lyaJesus , oge na uuyelele wondjokonona yi li paushili mboka wa pumbiwa .
Ngele owe ga lesha nuukeka otage ku pe uushili kutya iiningwanima mbika oya ningwa shili .
Eitaalo lyoye otali vulu okunkondopala ngele owa tseya kutya omolwashike iinima mbika ya ningwa .
Tacitus , a valwa momumvo 55 E.N . Okwa nyola a ti : “ Kristus , hoka kwa za edhina [ Aakriste ] , okwa li a hepekwa noonkondo pethimbo lyepangelo lyaTiberius , kugumwe gwomaapanguli yetu , Pontius Pilatus . ”
Jesus okwa popiwa wo kuSuetonius gwomethelemumvo lyotango ( okuza pomumvo 1 - 100 ) ; komunandjokonona Omujuda Josephus gwomethelemumvo lyotango ( okuza pomumvo 1 - 100 ) ; nokuPliny the Younger , omupangeli gwaBitinia ngoka a li ko petameko lyethelemumvo etiyali ( okuza pomumvo 101 - 200 ) .
( 1 Petrus 1 : 24 , 25 ) Onkee ano , itashi vulika naanaa aapataneki oyendji yaJesus ya nyole omahokololo ngoka taga ningitha aantu yi itaale Jesus nokukala ye mu inekela .
Shi na ko nasha neyumuko lyaJesus , gumwe gwomaayapostoli ye , Petrus , okwe shi yelitha a ti : “ Kalunga okwe mu yumudha kuusi esiku etitatu nokwe mu hololele aantu . Oye ini ihololela aantu ayehe , ihe otse ashike mboka Kalunga e tu hogolola nale , tu kale oonzapo dhe . Otse otwa lile notwa ninwe pamwe naye , sho a yumuka kuusi . ”
Evaangeli lyaMateus olya popya kutya sho aayambi aakuluntu yu uvu kombinga yeyumuko lyaJesus , oya li ya keelele onkundana ndjoka kaayi taandele . Aayambi aakuluntu oya li aawiliki yomalongelokalunga noya li ye tonde Jesus . — Mateus 28 : 11 - 15 .
Mbela shika osha hala okutya Jesus okwa li a hala eyumuko lye kaali tseyike ?
Aawe . Petrus okwa tsikile ko a ti : “ Okwe tu lombwele , tu uvithile aantu ayehe evaangeli notu tseyithile aantu ayehe kutya Kalunga okwa lenge Jesus , a ninge omupanguli gwaanamwenyo naasi . ”
Aakriste yashili oya kala nokuuvitha kombinga yeyumuko lyaJesus nokunena otaya tsikile oku shi ninga . — Iilonga 10 : 42 .
Onkee ano eso olya taandele maantu ayehe , oshoka ayehe oya yono . ” ​ — Aaroma 5 : 12
Oto katya ngiini uuna wa pulwa kutya , “ Mbela owa hala okukala nomwenyo sigo aluhe ? ”
Aantu oyendji otashi vulika ya tye eeno , ihe natango otashi vulika ya kale yu uvite kutya shoka kashi shi shoshili noinatu pumbwa okwiipula kombinga yasho .
Eso oli li oshitopolwa shonkalamwenyo , yamwe osho haya ti ngaaka , oli li oshinima shopaunshitwe okuza keshito lyetu .
Natu tye nee , epulo ndyoka olya lundululwa , e tali pulwa taku ti : “ Mbela owa hala okusa ngashingeyi ? ”
Shampa we li pulwa wu li monkalo ombwanawa oto ka yamukula kutya aawe , ngaashi naanaa aantu oyendji haya yamukula .
Ombiimbeli otayi tu lombwele kutya Kalunga okwa shita aantu nehalo lyokukala nomwenyo sigo aluhe .
Nokuli otayi ti kutya , “ [ Kalunga ] okwa tula uukwaaluhe moomwenyo dhaantu . ” — Omuuvithi 3 : 11 .
Kunena aantu ihaya kala nomwenyo sigo aluhe .
Mbela Kalunga okwa ninga po elongekidho lyontumba a mangulule mo aantu monkalo ndjoka ?
Omayamukulo gopaMbiimbeli komapulo ngoka otaga nyanyudha omitima , notaga yelitha nawa kutya omolwashike Jesus a li a hepekwa nokudhipagwa .
Oontopolwa ndatu dhopetameko dhembo lyOmbiimbeli lyotango lyaGenesis , otadhi tu lombwele kutya Kalunga okwa li a pe aaihokani yotango , Adam naEve , etegameno lyokukala nomwenyo sigo aluhe .
Okwa li wo e ya lombwele kutya oshike ye na okuninga , opo ya kale ye gu na .
Ehokololo otali popi wo nkene ya li inaaya vulika kuKalunga e taya kanitha etegameno ndyoka .
Ngaashi owala Omavaangeli , Genesis naye oku na ehokololo li li paushili lyondjokonona yaantu .
Oshizemo osha li shini sho Adam inaa vulika ?
Ombiimbeli otayi ti : “ Uulunde owe etwa muuyuni komuntu gumwe [ Adam ] , nuulunde we owe etelele eso . Onkee ano eso olya taandele maantu ayehe , oshoka ayehe oya yono . ”
Kungawo , Adam okwa kanitha etegameno lyokukala nomwenyo sigo aluhe , nolwahugunina okwa ka sa .
Molwashoka tse oyana , otwa thigulula uulunde we .
Mbela Kalunga ota ka ninga po sha , opo aantu ya mangululwe mo monkalo ndjoka ?
Odhoshili kutya Kalunga okwa ninga po elongekidho , opo a mangulule nenge a futile po shoka sha kanithwa kuAdam omolwoluvalo lwe , ano etegameno lyomwenyo gwaluhe .
Ombiimbeli otayi ti : “ Eso olyo ondjambi yuulunde , ” Aaroma 6 : 23 .
Shika osha hala okutya oshizemo shuulunde osho eso .
Sha faathana , ohatu yono nohatu si omolwuulunde .
Nonando twa valwa aalunde , kashi shi epuko lyetu .
Onkee ano , Kalunga okwa tumu pahole Omwana omuholike , Jesus , ‘ a se opo etu kulile mo muulunde ’ wetu .
Molwashoka Adam okwa li omuntu a gwanenena ( kee na uulunde ) .
Okwe tu etela uulunde nosho wo eso omolwokwaavulika kwe , ihe opwa li pwa pumbiwa omuntu a gwanenena ngoka a li omuvuliki sigo omeso lye , opo e tu mangulule mo momutengi ngoka .
Ombiimbeli otayi shi yelitha ngeyi : “ Ngaashi aantu ayehe ya ningi aalunde omolwokwaavulika kwomuntu gumwe , ano osho tuu oyendji otaa ningwa aayuuki koshipala shaKalunga omolwokuvulika kwomuntu gumwe . ”
Okwa thigi po olukalwa lwe megulu * , e ta ningi omuntu a gwanenena , ngoka a si peha lyetu .
Oshizemo , otatu vulu okukala aayuuki koshipala shaKalunga nokukala tu na etegameno lyoku ka mona omwenyo gwaaluhe .
Omolwashike nduno sha li sha pumbiwa Jesus a se , opo shika shi vule okugwanithwa ?
Omolwashike Kalunga Omunankondoawike ngoka e li omupangeli inaa keelela uupyakadhi mbuka wu ye sigo okoluvalo lwaAdam , opo lu kale nomwenyo sigo aluhe ?
Kalunga okwa tula po uuyuki moshinima shika , naantu otashi vulika ya kale ya kumwa ngele ote ke shi ninga miinima yilwe ishewe .
Pashiholelwa , mbela ota ka tokola ngaa shili pauyuuki sho ta ka tala kutya oolye yomoyana yaAdam ya gwana okupewa omwenyo gwaaluhe ?
Mbela otatu vulu ngaa okwiinekela muye kutya ota ka gwanitha po omauvaneko ge ?
Okuvulika kuye nokulonga uuyuki we omolwehupitho lyetu , Kalunga ote tu shilipaleke kutya aluhe oha ningi shoka shu uka .
Omolweyambo lyeso lyaJesus , Kalunga okwe tu pe etegameno lyomwenyo gwaaluhe mOparadisa kombanda yevi .
Ndhindhilika oohapu dhaJesus ndhoka dhi li muJohannes 3 : 16 tadhi ti : “ Oshoka osho ngeyi Kalunga a kala e hole uuyuni , oye a gandja Omwana awike , opo shaa ngoka te mu itaale , kaa kane , ihe a kale e na omwenyo gwaaluhe . ”
Eso lyaJesus otali popi oshindji kaashi shi owala kombinga yuuyuki waKalunga wa dhenga mbanda , ihe ope na wo oshindji unene tuu , ohole ye yokuhola aantu .
Omolwashike Jesus a li a hepekwa nokudhipagwa momukalo gu nyanyalitha ngaashi gwa hokololwa mOmavaangeli ?
Sho Jesus i idhidhimikile omamakelo noonkalo ondhigu oku ulike kutya Satana omuniifundja sho a ti kutya aantu itaya vulu okukala adhiginini kuKalunga uuna ye li momamakelo .
( Job 2 : 4 , 5 ) Omapopyo ngoka otashi vulika ga monike ga fa ge li mondjila konima sho Satana a ningitha Adam ngoka a li a gwanenena a yone .
Jesus oku thike pamwe nAdam ngoka naye a li a gwanenena , ihe Jesus okwa kala omudhiginini , nonando okwa li ta monithwa iihuna noonkondo .
( 1 Aakorinto 15 : 45 ) Jesus oku ulike kutya Adam okwa li ta vulu okuhogolola okukala omudhiginini kuKalunga , molwaashoka okwa li ta vulu oku shi ninga .
Mokwiidhidhimikila omahepeko , Jesus okwe tu tulila po oshinkoti shoka tu na okulandula .
( 1 Petrus 2 : 21 ) omolwevuliko lye Kalunga okwe mu pe ondjambi yomwenyo gwa gwanenena megulu moka itaa ka sa .
Jesus okwe tu lombwela shoka tu na okuninga sho a ti : “ Mboka ye ku tseya , Kalunga awike kashili , noya tseya wo Jesus Kristus , ngoka we mu tumu , oyo mboka ye na omwenyo gwaaluhe . ” — Johannes 17 : 3 .
Aanyanyangidhi yoshifo shika otaye ku indile wu ilonge oshindji kombinga yaJehova , Kalunga kashili nosho wo kombinga yOmwana , Jesus Kristus .
Oonzapo dhaJehova dhomoshitopolwa sheni otadhi ka kala dha nyanyukwa oku ku kwathela .
Oto vulu wo natango okumona uuyelele wulwe ngele wa yi kepandja lyetu lyokointaneta , www.jw.org / ng .
Tala oshitopolwa “ The Historical Character of Genesis , ” membo Insight on the Scriptures , ” epandja 922 , lya nyanyangidhwa kOonzapo dhaJehova .
Kalunga sho a lundululile omwenyo gwOmwana moshivalelo shomukadhona Maria , okwa ningi omusimba , nombepo yaKalunga oya li ya gamene Jesus , opo kaathigulule uulunde washa kuMaria . — Lukas 1 : 31 , 35 .
Ongulohi ndjoka manga Jesus inaa yamba po omwenyo gwe , okwa li a gongala pamwe naayapostoli ye aadhiginini nokwa li a dhike po Edhimbuluko lyeso lye .
Oye okwa ti kuyo : “ Shi ningeni nokudhimbulukwa ndje . ”
( Lukas 22 : 19 ) Oonzapo dhaJehova muuyuni awuhe ohadhi vulika kelombwelo ndyoka . Ohadhi gongala pamwe dhi dhimbulukwe eso lyaJesus .
Nuumvo , Edhimbuluko lyeso lyaJesus otali ka kala ko mEtitatu , 23 Maalitsa , konima ngele etango lya ningine .
Pomweelo itapu futilwa sha ; noitapu ka umbwa ongalo .
Pula Oonzapo dhaJehova moshitopolwa sheni dhi ku lombwele ethimbo nehala mpoka tapu ka ningilwa oshiningwanima shika .
