Omayamukulo komapulo ngoka kage shi omadhigu .
Shoka otatu vulu oku shi mona mwaashoka Ombiimbeli tayi ti kombinga yoondunge nowino .
Omayeletumbulo 3 : 13 - 15 otaga ti : “ Omunelago omuntu ngoka a likola owino , nomuntu ngoka a pewa oondunge .
Oshoka oku dhi likola okuwanawa ku vule oshisiliveli , notadhi etitha ontanitho yi vule ndjoka yoshingoli .
Jesus Kristus okwe tu tulila po oshiholelwa oshiwanawa shokukala aanashili .
Ndi li omuwiliki gwehangano , onda li nda tegelelwa ndi ninge euvathano naangoka hatu futu kuye iihohela moku mu pa ombumbo , opo kaa lopote ehangano lyetu sho ihaali futu iihohela yi igwana po .
Kungawo , onda kala nda talika ko kaandi shi omunashili .
Sho nda tseya oshili , onde etha po iilonga mbyoka , nonando onda li he futwa nawa .
Onda tulila po aamwandjemati yaali oshiholelwa oshiwanawa nondi na iinakugwanithwa megongalo .
Aayaluli yiihohela nosho wo mboka handi longo nayo oya tala ndje ko ndi li omunashili . ”
Rut okwa yi kuIsraeli , hoka a ka longela Kalunga kashili .
